{"tid":2194463,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真點頂上之對決，聖馬力諾對列支敦士登","createTime":"2020-09-08T13:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T14:54:47.000Z","uid":34572,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9598916922fa37073298ec2058060dbb74742850","tid":2194463,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYR5anS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYR5anS.png&h=60cb2749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港時間0245<br />\n<br />\n上場直布羅陀雖然排名上係歐洲第二廢，但其實論近年進退步嚟計，列支敦士登比直布羅陀再低少少。為咗證明世界排名名符其實係高過直布羅陀，列支敦士登一定會出盡全力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而聖馬力諾同史上惟一勝仗嘅對手重逢，絕對唔會手軟，力爭歷史第二勝同埋史上正式比賽第一勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb18362edc254059c352f047bdfd6935e398018","tid":2194463,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"加埋摩納哥Monaco, 安道爾Andorra, 可以開一枱麻雀"},{"pid":"e47e50991117fcd2fd4520a31e5064f4f2f9c83d","tid":2194463,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"aeb18362edc254059c352f047bdfd6935e398018","tid":2194463,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"加埋摩納哥Monaco, 安道爾Andorra, 可以開一枱麻雀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:50:18.000Z","msg":"monaco法甲踢得唔差"},{"pid":"7389ff9ee586dd00fe8dc47590289d46c61a04a1","tid":2194463,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:53:51.000Z","msg":"聖馬力諾其實係咪個國家搞賭波搵食"},{"pid":"4484ae2cfe8bb4f4bb565de25a9ddef8ecb30a30","tid":2194463,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"supp